root: ^[Angel]Hey, so, uh, what got you into tattooing?
^So, is it something you always wanted to do, or was it something you stumbled into?
^I'm not saying that tattooing is something you picked as a last resort. I mean--
^Ow! Can you be a bit more gentle?
^[Sam]Stay still, I don't wanna make a mistake.
^Do you have a girlfriend? Ghh--I swear you just went harder.
^I'm not hitting on your, I'm just trying to make conversation. Unless you're into me? In which case, we can always find a room.
